				<div class="comment-body"><p>Instant-runoff elections are also arguably much like what we see every year on American Idol and all other such elimination contests, only set up so that only one expensive public election is necessary to collect the voter-opinion information to support all of the eliminations.</p>
<p>There&#8217;s a pretty good three-minute video walkthrough of instant-runoff voting at <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wqblOq8BmgM" rel="nofollow">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wqblOq8BmgM</a></p>
</div>

